lead_paragraph: Son Heung-min has struggled to maintain the form that saw him named Premier League player of the month for September but the Tottenham Hotspur striker says his mental strength will be key in South Korea's World Cup qualifier against Uzbekistan.

headline.print_headline: South Korea's Son Keen to Shake of Scoring Blues
